h2.div: IMPORTANT NOTICE: School Closed for Remainder of 19-20 SY

div.p: Governor Walz has ordered schools to remain closed through the remainder of the 19-20 school year with Distance Learning in place in order to flatten the curve and decrease the spread of Covid-19. It is recommended that people should continue social distancing practices and only travel when it is essential.
